title: Jim Carrey's Ex Took Her Life by Overdosing on Drugs Prescribed to Him
text:
Photos 
MELBOURNE: Jim Carrey’s former girlfriend, who committed suicide few days after breaking up with him, reportedly took her life by overdosing on drugs prescribed to the comedian. 
According to sources, the 28-year-old Irish makeup artist overdosed on three medications - the painkiller Percocet, sleep aid Ambien and blood-pressure medication Propranolol, reports News.com.au. 
Empty bottles of the drugs were found at Cathriona White’s bedside in her LA home at the time of her suicide. 
Carrey broke up with White on September 24.
